  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink261-kilavi">allakuṟippaṭṭut talaimakaṉ nīṅkiṉamai aṟiyātāḷ pōṉṟu tōḻi piṟṟai ñāṉṟ avaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉāy niṟpat talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">
          

What the confidante, who pretended not to know that the hero had been misled by a false sign and had left, told the heroine, as the hero stood behind the hedge on a later day.
            
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink261">
<l>meṉṟiṉai mēynta taṟukaṭ paṉṟi</l>
<l>vaṉka laṭukkattut tuñcu nāṭa</l>
<l>ṉentai yaṟita lañcikko</l>
<l>latuvē maṉṟa vārā maiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Did the man from the land where</l>
        <l>cruel boars that graze on tender millet,</l>
        <l>sleep on the mountain slopes with hard stones,</l>
        <l rend="space">not come,</l>
        <l>having feared</l>
        <l>that my father would know?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
